---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Me & Resume — Annalisa Ard"
  description="About Annalisa Ard — Narrative Designer, Mythologist Connoisseur, Literature Expert, and Adventure Seeker."
>
  <section class="section cover about-hero">
    <div
      class="cover-bg"
      style="background-image: url('/images/about/mayan-ruins-be5208.jpg');"
    ></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <h1 class="hero-title">About Annalisa</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Narrative Designer, Mythologist Connoisseur, Literature Expert, and
        Adventure Seeker
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bio-section">
    <div class="bio-grid">
      <aside class="portrait-col">
        <img
          class="portrait"
          src="/images/about/annalisa-ard-73ebb1.jpg"
          alt="Annalisa Ard"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <a href="/files/ard-resume.pdf" class="resume-link" download>
          Annalisa's Resume
        </a>
      </aside>

      <div class="bio-col">
        <p class="bio-lead">
          I'm a narrative designer with a lifelong obsession for storytelling
          that gives players real choices, and real consequences. My mission
          is to create emotionally resonant, reactive experiences in all forms
          of RPGs that feel intimate yet open.
        </p>
        <p>
          Before stepping into the game industry, I spent nearly a decade
          teaching literature, mythology, and narrative structure to students
          around the world. That background trained me to dissect story arcs,
          communicate complex ideas clearly, and adapt tales dynamically to
          diverse audiences — skills I now channel into crafting branching
          dialogue, reactive quests, and worlds that feel alive.
        </p>
        <p>
          In 2025, I wrote and directed over 2,000 hours of interactive
          narrative content for multiplayer campaigns, honing my ability to
          design with player agency at the core. My work emphasizes pacing,
          emotional payoff, and cross-department collaboration, because the
          best narratives aren't written in isolation.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm especially inspired by the CRPG's interest and commitment to
          storytelling that rewards curiosity, punishes assumptions, and
          honors player choice with tangible narrative impact. Playing and
          studying the leading games is a master class in collaborative
          worldbuilding and emergent design. It would be a dream, and a
          calling, to contribute to your next masterpiece.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    min-height: 75vh;
  }
  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.92);
    max-width: 900px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 4em;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: capitalize;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
    text-shadow: 0 0.05em 0.1em rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    margin: 0 0 0.4em;
  }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.7em;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: rgba(9, 15, 0, 0.95);
    text-shadow: 0 0.05em 0.1em rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .bio-section {
    padding-top: 8vh;
    padding-bottom: 8vh;
  }
  .bio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(220px, 1fr) 2.6fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .portrait-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 2rem;
  }
  .portrait {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 320px;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
  }
  .resume-link {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.8em;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .resume-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent-hover);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .bio-col p {
    font-size: 1.15em;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1.3em;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .bio-lead {
    font-size: 1.3em !important;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .bio-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
    .portrait-col {
      position: static;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.6em;
    }
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }
  }
</style>
